codePut:
UPDATE SKBHINS
SET SKBHINS_SSDT_CODE_NEWENT = :SKBHINS_SSDT_CODE_NEWENT
WHERE SKBHINS_PIDM = :parm_user_pidm
codeGet:
SELECT SKBHINS_PIDM AS ID, 
SKBHINS_SSDT_CODE_NEWENT,
SKBHINS_SSDT_CODE_DISALL,
SKBHINS_SSDT_CODE_PARED,
SKBHINS_SSDT_CODE_DOMICILE,
SKBHINS_SSDT_CODE_QUALENT3,
SKBHINS_SSDT_CODE_PREVINST
FROM SKBHINS
WHERE SKBHINS_NUMHUS = 1
AND SKBHINS_PIDM = :parm_user_pidm
